      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so something weird happened and i cant stop thinking about it. i was looking at this cracked coffee mug at a cafe today and for a split second it looked like... i dont know... like a specific pattern of red and blue lights, like emergency vehicles. then like ten mins later i look at my phone and there was a massive multi-car accident on the highway with sirens everywhere. it felt like the mug was showing me the event before it actually happened. do u think that's possible or am i just losing it?",
